data.description: FULLY FURNISHED and ASSESSMENT PAID. As you step inside this 2/2, you will be greeted by the breathtaking views of the tropical nature preserve of Estero Bay and skyline from Fort Myers Beach to Bonita Springs. Large tiled lanai with no-see-um screens allows you to enjoy these surroundings. For your convenience and peace of mind, electric storm shutters are installed on the lanai and guest bedroom. Inside, luxury vinyl tile flooring flows seamlessly throughout the living, dining, kitchen, and laundry areas. The entire unit has been freshly painted and features crown molding that adds an elegant touch to every room. Brand New AC in 2023.  The master bedroom boasts a spacious walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a seamless glass shower with tiled enclosure, custom vanity storage and backlit mirrors. The second bedroom, with twin beds, also offers ample storage space with a generous closet. Kitchen features brand new SS appliances with quartz counter and custom cabinets, new faucet and instant hot water dispenser. Condo also has an underneath oversized garage and storage area. Pay as you Play Golf! Lexington Country Club has a range of amenities and is a 24-hr. gated community located within minutes of beaches, shopping and medical facilities.
